      "side": 1,
      "message": "I see. It creates a GrProgramInfo with an empty processor set.\n\nHow does the appliedClip factor in? If you call visitProxies() after creating the pipeline, then GrPipeline::visitProxies visits the clip FPs. If it gets called before, do the clip FPs get visited from somewhere else?",
